{"id":177,"parent_id":158,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":177,"title":"Deuteronomy 19","subtitle":"","short_title":"Deut.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 19"],[".studySummary",["i","Cities of refuge are appointed for cases of manslaughter—Murderers will be put to death—Two or three witnesses are required in court cases—False witnesses will be punished."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.1","order":"02.06.019.15997"},["b","1"],"When the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God hath cut off the nations, whose land the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"thou succeedest"],"them, and dwellest in their cities, and in their houses;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.2","order":"02.06.019.15998"},["b","2"],"Thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"separate"],"three",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"cities"],"for thee in the midst of thy land, which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee to possess it."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.3","order":"02.06.019.15999"},["b","3"],"Thou shalt prepare thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"a way"],", and divide the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"coasts"],"of thy land, which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee to inherit, into three parts, that every slayer may",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"flee"],"thither."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.4","order":"02.06.019.16000"},["b","4"],"¶And this",["i","is"],"the case of the slayer, which shall flee thither, that he may live: Whoso killeth his neighbour",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"ignorantly"],", whom he hated not in time past;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.5","order":"02.06.019.16001"},["b","5"],"As when a man goeth into the wood with his neighbour to hew wood, and his hand fetcheth a stroke with the axe to cut down the tree, and the head slippeth from the helve, and lighteth upon his neighbour, that he die; he shall flee unto one of those cities, and live:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.6","order":"02.06.019.16002"},["b","6"],"Lest the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"avenger"],"of the blood pursue the slayer, while his heart is hot, and overtake him, because the way is long, and slay him; whereas he",["i","was"],"not worthy of death, inasmuch as he hated him not in time past."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.7","order":"02.06.019.16003"},["b","7"],"Wherefore I command thee, saying, Thou shalt separate three cities for thee."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.8","order":"02.06.019.16004"},["b","8"],"And if the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God enlarge thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"coast"],", as he hath sworn unto thy fathers, and give thee all the land which he promised to give unto thy fathers;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.9","order":"02.06.019.16005"},["b","9"],"If thou shalt keep all these commandments to do them, which I command thee this day, to love the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, and to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"walk"],"ever in his ways; then shalt thou add three cities more for thee, beside these three:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.10","order":"02.06.019.16006"},["b","10"],"That innocent blood be not shed in thy land, which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee",["i","for"],"an inheritance, and",["i","so"],"blood be upon thee."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.11","order":"02.06.019.16007"},["b","11"],"¶But if any man hate his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"neighbour"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"lie"],"in wait for him, and rise up against him, and smite him mortally that he die, and fleeth into one of these cities:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.12","order":"02.06.019.16008"},["b","12"],"Then the elders of his city shall send and fetch him thence, and deliver him into the hand of the avenger of blood, that he may die."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.13","order":"02.06.019.16009"},["b","13"],"Thine eye shall not pity him, but thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"put away"],["i","the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"guilt"],"of"],"innocent blood from Israel, that it may go well with thee."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.14","order":"02.06.019.16010"},["b","14"],"¶Thou shalt not remove thy neighbour’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"landmark"],", which they of old time have set in thine inheritance, which thou shalt inherit in the land that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee to possess it."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.15","order":"02.06.019.16011"},["b","15"],"¶One",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"witness"],"shall not rise up against a man for any iniquity, or for any sin, in any sin that he sinneth: at the mouth of two",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"witnesses"],", or at the mouth of three witnesses, shall the matter be established."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.16","order":"02.06.019.16012"},["b","16"],"¶If a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"false witness"],"rise up against any man to testify against him",["i","that which is"],"wrong;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.17","order":"02.06.019.16013"},["b","17"],"Then both the men, between whom the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"controversy"],["i","is,"],"shall stand before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", before the priests and the judges, which shall be in those days;"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.18","order":"02.06.019.16014"},["b","18"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"judges"],"shall make diligent inquisition: and, behold,",["i","if"],"the witness",["i","be"],"a false witness,",["i","and"],"hath testified falsely against his brother;"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.19","order":"02.06.019.16015"},["b","19"],"Then shall ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"do"],"unto him, as he had thought to have done unto his brother: so shalt thou put the evil away from among you."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.20","order":"02.06.019.16016"},["b","20"],"And those which remain shall hear, and fear, and shall henceforth commit no more any such evil among you."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.21","order":"02.06.019.16017"},["b","21"],"And thine eye shall not pity;",["i","but"],"life",["i","shall go"],"for life,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"eye for eye"],", tooth for tooth, hand for hand, foot for foot."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.1a","order":"02.06.019.16018"},["b","1a"],["span.small","HEB"],"you dispossess."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.2a","order":"02.06.019.16020"},["b","2a"],["span.small","OR"],"set apart (also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.7"},"v. 7"],")."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.2b","order":"02.06.019.16022"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/21.13"},"Ex. 21:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.3a","order":"02.06.019.16024"},["b","3a"],["span.small","HEB"],"roads."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.3b","order":"02.06.019.16026"},["b","3b"],["span.small","HEB"],"area, territory (also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.8"},"v. 8"],")."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.3c","order":"02.06.019.16028"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/21.13.12-14"},"Ex. 21:13 (12–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.4a","order":"02.06.019.16030"},["b","4a"],["span.small","HEB"],"unintentionally."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.6a","order":"02.06.019.16032"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.23"},"D&C 98:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.8a","order":"02.06.019.16034"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/4.10"},"1 Chr. 4:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.9a","order":"02.06.019.16036"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.11a","order":"02.06.019.16038"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.24"},"Deut. 27:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.35"},"2 Ne. 9:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.21"},"Mosiah 13:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.11b","order":"02.06.019.16040"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/35.16.16-25"},"Num. 35:16 (16–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.13a","order":"02.06.019.16042"},["b","13a"],["span.small","HEB"],"purge."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.13b","order":"02.06.019.16044"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/2.31"},"1 Kgs. 2:31"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/guilt"},"TG Guilt"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.14a","order":"02.06.019.16046"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/27.17"},"Deut. 27:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.2"},"Job 24:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/22.28"},"Prov. 22:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/5.10"},"Hosea 5:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.15a","order":"02.06.019.16048"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/26.60"},"Matt. 26:60"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/5.19"},"1 Tim. 5:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.15b","order":"02.06.019.16050"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/13.1"},"2 Cor. 13:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.12.12,14"},"2 Ne. 27:12 (12, 14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.28"},"D&C 6:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.16a","order":"02.06.019.16052"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lying"},"TG Lying"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.17a","order":"02.06.019.16054"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disputations"},"TG Disputations"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.18a","order":"02.06.019.16056"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/7.25"},"Ezra 7:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.19a","order":"02.06.019.16058"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/retribution"},"TG Retribution"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.21a","order":"02.06.019.16060"},["b","21a"],["span.small","IE"],"not literally; interpreted by the Rabbis to be symbolic of equal compensation."]]}
